titles.title: A resolution commending David J. Tinsley on his service to the United States Senate.
A resolution commending David J. Tinsley on his service to the United States Senate.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary:
(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)
Declares that the Senate expresses its appreciation to Dave Tinsley and commends him for his lengthy, faithful, and outstanding service.
